     H            Y.
     F** GDGR90 **********************************
     F*  IMPORT ORDER DATA REFORMATION (PRODUCT) *
     F*                    K.YASUDA   2000.06.29 *
     F********************************** GDGR90 **
     FGDGPP15 IP  E                    DISK
     FGDGWP90 O   E                    DISK
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80ICSKHZ
     I                                        1   40ICSKYY
     I                                        5   60ICSKMM
     I                                        7   80ICSKDD
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80ICODHZ
     I                                        1   40ICODRY
     I                                        5   60ICODRM
     I                                        7   80ICODRD
      *------*
      * PARM *
      *------*
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PHIZK   8
     C                     PARM           PRECD   7
     C                     PARM           PKENS   7
     C                     MOVELPHIZK     @HIZK   80
      *
     C                     ADD  1         WRECD   70
     C           ICODHZ    IFLE @HIZK
     C                     GOTO SKIP
     C                     END
      *
     C                     ADD  1         WKENS   70
     C                     WRITEGDGWP901
      *
     C           SKIP      TAG
      *
     CLR                   MOVE WRECD     PRECD
     CLR                   MOVE WKENS     PKENS
